- `gray-850` - Card hover states (custom)
- `gray-800` - Selected items
- `gray-700` - Borders
- `gray-600` - Disabled states
- `gray-400` - Secondary text
- `blue-600` - Primary buttons
- `red-600` - Destructive actions

